1.name: First release
1.desc:
User message approved and issued in the first release of the year of
                                    the UNTDID (United Nations Trade Data Interchange Directory); valid for directories
                                    published prior to March 1990. Service message approved and issued as the first
                                    release of the message within a version of ISO 9735; valid for version 4 of IS0 9735
                                    and later.

2.name: Second release
2.desc:
User message approved and issued in the second release of the year of
                                    the UNTDID (United Nations Trade Data Interchange Directory); valid for directories
                                    published prior to March 1990. Service message approved and issued as the second
                                    release of the message within a version of ISO 9735; valid for version 4 of IS0 9735
                                    and later.
